Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.46,0:00:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切开始于神木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.56,0:00:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断战斗\N不断祈求  不断寻找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.57,0:00:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从中产生了强烈的羁绊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.44,0:00:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全新的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.47,0:00:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明的未来从现在开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.94,0:00:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要消灭拥有不死身的奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.87,0:00:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.54,0:00:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  桔梗与奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.34,0:00:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉与我们之间的因缘纠葛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.05,0:00:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将全部在此交会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.75,0:00:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引导我们的最后一块碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.48,0:00:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枯井的另一边\N战国的世界里还有明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.89,0:00:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战国时代的传说故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.19,0:00:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.19,0:00:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为谁而流的眼泪祈祷般地流下脸颊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.43,0:00:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隐藏脆弱  温柔地接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.07,0:00:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连呼吸都忘记  眼中的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.08,0:00:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有太阳闪耀着 不断寻找着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.05,0:01:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝视镜子 你一定能看见立誓的那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.72,0:01:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的背后也有翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.90,0:01:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的改变  将改变世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.74,0:01:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现梦想的爱的火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.14,0:01:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越虚幻的海市蜃楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.52,0:01:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空有光  大地有水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.42,0:01:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚强的心灵带你到未来的ANGELUS（奉告祈祷）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.10,0:01:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双手握紧热情的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.59,0:02:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是宿蛹的尸体耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.27,0:02:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这么看来\N村民的传言是真的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.04,0:02:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说七天前这里的一座山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在一夕之间就消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.07,0:02:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说这件事\N跟宿蛹有什么关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.58,0:02:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很微弱\N但是还残留着奈落的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.38,0:02:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有妖怪的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.98,0:02:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都还附着在这里的地面上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.49,0:02:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第165话\N消灭奈落最重要的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.10,0:02:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪来那么多宿蛹\N不管怎么杀都杀不完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.91,0:03:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到虫子的巢穴了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.61,0:03:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.05,0:03:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这些虫子\N究竟是什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.62,0:03:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们是宿蛹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.79,0:03:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.46,0:03:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种宿蛹应该是\N寄生在大型的妖怪体内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在外面筑巢实在很少见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对这种事倒是挺清楚的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是知道些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.70,0:03:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再装了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你\N为什么奈落那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.97,0:03:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令我们一发现宿蛹\N就马上除掉它们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.24,0:03:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.65,0:03:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最猛胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.55,0:03:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我们回去了  走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的一点风声都没听到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.92,0:03:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是深得奈落的信赖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.03,0:03:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是我多心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.87,0:03:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我的确感觉到山移动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.48,0:04:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.31,0:04:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些宿蛹失去了原本的归属
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.38,0:04:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说它们再也无法\N栖息在大型的妖怪体内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.72,0:04:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落之所以命令我们\N一旦看到宿蛹就要杀掉它们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.69,0:04:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不想让别人发现这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.73,0:04:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移动的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.80,0:04:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那就是\N宿蛹们的寄生体的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.44,0:04:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人的毛病\N就是喜欢擅作主张跑出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.01,0:04:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没有错  那座山是活着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.51,0:04:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落那个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.65,0:04:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次又有什么阴谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.58,0:04:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.09,0:04:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落为什么要让\N那个不可信任的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.26,0:04:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀  这是奈落下的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你去协助神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.53,0:05:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.33,0:05:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近了  是妖怪的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  你看那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.68,0:05:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山好像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在移动耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.13,0:05:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.13,0:05:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛突然动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.87,0:05:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是奈落的手下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.21,0:05:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了奈落是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.21,0:05:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个打扰我的睡眠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.31,0:05:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钻进我的体内的\N那个愚蠢家伙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.52,0:05:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.15,0:05:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落钻进了这个妖怪的体内…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.45,0:06:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我吸入了太多\N那家伙所释放出来的瘴气和妖气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.83,0:06:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我被迫\N从两百年的沉睡中苏醒过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.46,0:06:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.83,0:06:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙抢走了\N我体内的守护石之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.80,0:06:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就逃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.17,0:06:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.34,0:06:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁敢把他藏起来我绝不饶他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.11,0:06:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.18,0:06:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就找奈落这个目标而言\N我们可是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.75,0:06:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点告诉我奈落的去向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.35,0:06:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然我心中的怒气\N绝对无法平息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟你说了不知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在也在找奈落啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.36,0:06:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说\N被奈落抢走了守护石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.36,0:06:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个守护石是什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是能保护我岳山人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.83,0:06:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以山岳的型态\N存在于这个世上的石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.57,0:06:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也是能保护我\N以山岳的型态沉睡的石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.77,0:06:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妖璧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妖璧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岳山人大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.44,0:06:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妖璧不正是镇住你的石头吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.28,0:07:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能消除我的妖气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以让外敌不会接近我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.79,0:07:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让我免于世俗中\N无谓争斗的守护石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.29,0:07:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将妖气…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.79,0:07:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.29,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说\N要是能把不妖璧弄到手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落的妖气也就能被消除吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.73,0:07:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道奈落是为了不被我们找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.30,0:07:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫做不妖璧的东西\N是长什么样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.97,0:07:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么颜色  有什么气味吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是想帮你抢回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.81,0:07:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种废话  我才不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.75,0:07:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的\N还在生起床气的臭老头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.25,0:07:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子跟你的对话\N好像也只能到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.14,0:07:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.07,0:07:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.84,0:07:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不杀我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.91,0:08:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该杀得了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.78,0:08:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么想被杀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.72,0:08:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.15,0:08:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们互相残杀\N根本没有任何的意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.52,0:08:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人只有奈落一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.02,0:08:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们在找奈落的时候\N要是找到了不妖璧的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.86,0:08:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会还给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.36,0:08:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.47,0:08:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.60,0:08:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.94,0:08:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的妖气结晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一小片就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当它接近不妖璧的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.21,0:08:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结晶的妖气就会消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.51,0:08:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开之后妖气又会恢复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.92,0:08:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这将成为\N我们寻找奈落的重要线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.86,0:08:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这样看来\N他好像是信任我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.33,0:08:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…真的很谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.43,0:08:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你们快去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.87,0:09:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话又说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.97,0:09:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落那个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.10,0:09:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要抢走\N不妖璧那种东西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是有什么用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.84,0:09:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.58,0:09:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要找出奈落的下落\N已经是很困难的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为什么还有必要\N把妖气给消除掉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.89,0:09:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.99,0:09:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落那家伙\N一定是打算利用不妖璧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.96,0:09:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那婴儿的妖气封住\N隐藏他的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.11,0:09:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.98,0:09:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神无应该是跟那个婴儿在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.78,0:09:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于可以知道他们的藏身之处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.22,0:09:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐说过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能够找到那个婴儿\N就能杀死奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我收拾掉那个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.63,0:10:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗大人的灵发解开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.73,0:10:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近有什么东西吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.74,0:10:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.74,0:10:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是是谁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.42,0:10:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是奈落的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到有碎片的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.66,0:10:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一片  应该是琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.93,0:10:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.80,0:10:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.76,0:10:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是靠四魂之玉碎片\N在维系生命的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的生命\N是不是被奈落控制住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.27,0:10:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要听命于奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.31,0:10:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.98,0:10:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岳山人给我们的结晶\N妖气消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.09,0:11:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是因为\N前面不远处有不妖璧吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.19,0:11:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.92,0:11:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  奈落就在眼前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.09,0:11:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是这样\N连桔梗的气味都出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.57,0:11:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好久不见了  桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.33,0:11:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从白灵山一别以来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.70,0:11:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.31,0:11:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候  我原本的确以为我已经把你给杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.18,0:11:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天底下的事\N可不会事事如你所愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.31,0:11:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然没察觉到\N他就站在我的身后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不到他的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.32,0:11:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也无法\N从奈落身上感觉到妖气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.46,0:11:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是很想见到我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.87,0:11:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿不到下一支箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.24,0:11:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什么  琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.34,0:11:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去取桔梗的人头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.25,0:12:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在犹豫吗  琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.03,0:12:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.73,0:12:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然感觉不到奈落的妖力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是不妖璧的力量吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.03,0:12:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.40,0:12:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落  你这个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.74,0:12:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来净化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.55,0:12:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.55,0:12:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.29,0:12:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我太大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然感觉不到奈落身上的妖气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说他是为了袭击你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.97,0:12:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而去抢夺不妖璧的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.30,0:12:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妖璧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一种\N用来消除妖气的守护石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.44,0:13:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果奈落的目标\N是桔梗姑娘的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.08,0:13:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么轻易走掉\N还真是有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.05,0:13:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.46,0:13:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是发生这种事\N真的没有关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.60,0:13:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想桔梗姑娘\N应该是不会跟我们同行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.84,0:13:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟以前一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个人只是在话别吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.47,0:13:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是也太久了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.24,0:13:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.88,0:13:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我可以\N长时间跟犬夜叉在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.82,0:13:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是桔梗她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是话别也太久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在说些什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.99,0:13:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是\N刚才奈落只是在声东击西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.76,0:13:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我的式神\N找到了别的某个东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.50,0:14:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.77,0:14:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落中了我的箭\N最后还是没有死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.27,0:14:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从那个家伙\N从白灵山出来之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.34,0:14:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么攻击他的身体\N他都死不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.25,0:14:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为\N那家伙的心脏在别的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.15,0:14:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心脏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.29,0:14:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来要用不妖璧掩饰的东西\N是心脏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要彻底击倒奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.02,0:14:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么无论如何\N都要先找到他的心脏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.80,0:14:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.07,0:14:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不妖璧\N可以把你的妖气隐藏起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.91,0:14:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说他原来的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.94,0:14:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了不想被卷入\N无谓的纷争而使用它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你打算怎么使用它呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.19,0:15:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀你看  是人类的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.03,0:15:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.43,0:15:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎被大量吃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉他们的\N是个叫做“魄”的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.97,0:15:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去狩猎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.72,0:15:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剖开它的肚子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.09,0:15:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要伤及它的胃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.99,0:15:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.23,0:15:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发光的东西塞得满满的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是人类的魄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.57,0:15:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家伙把人类的魄\N当作食物吃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.64,0:15:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本以为\N只要有了这个妖气结晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.48,0:15:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以尽快追上奈落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落的心脏吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.08,0:15:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗是这么说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.39,0:15:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟桔梗说了半天\N就只说这些吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只说这些啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.09,0:16:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就只有说这些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.63,0:16:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么两个人\N还要偷偷摸摸的说话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.13,0:16:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.40,0:16:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得气氛有点沉重耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.77,0:16:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐一下吧\N这是常有的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.17,0:16:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有妖怪的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是妖怪的残骸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么\N像是东拼西凑出来的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.83,0:16:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么妖怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.06,0:16:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好像是\N由很多妖怪拼凑起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.57,0:16:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是妖怪的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.54,0:16:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那应该是魄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.51,0:16:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管人类  动物  还是妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.54,0:16:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有所谓的魂与魄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.08,0:16:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“魂”是心  就是所谓的“灵魂”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.01,0:17:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而“魄”是让身体活动的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.68,0:17:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个妖怪的魂出了什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.89,0:17:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是死的时候被夺走了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.72,0:17:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后它的身体\N只靠“魄”来活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.29,0:17:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体只要还有“魄”\N就算没有“魂”还是可以动的是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会不会也跟奈落有关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.97,0:17:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪的残骸\N已经四散到别的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.77,0:17:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来靠着魄到处跑的妖怪\N可能不只这一只
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.22,0:17:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.81,0:17:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.51,0:18:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多\N到处都是妖怪的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.45,0:18:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.09,0:18:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一只啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.75,0:18:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.86,0:18:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么觉得\N它们好像越来越近似人类了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.10,0:18:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.47,0:18:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟最初的拼凑妖怪比起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.44,0:18:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.70,0:18:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前为止我们遇到的妖怪\N简直就像是实验试作品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个气味\N是白童子那个小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就闻到这里来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.02,0:18:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白童子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.19,0:18:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这一次又在动什么歪脑筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.59,0:18:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就问问这个魍魉丸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.79,0:18:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.69,0:18:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个妖怪是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.70,0:18:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没错\N越来越接近人类的型态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.20,0:19:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了很多拼凑\N试着很多方式之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.34,0:19:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于明白还是人类的型态\N可以让它们更方便移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.37,0:19:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思也就是说人类的魄\N还是适合人类的型态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.61,0:19:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然又是你们干的好事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.38,0:19:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魍魉丸\N你就陪犬夜叉玩一玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.65,0:19:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白童子是不是想利用犬夜叉\N来试这个完成品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.32,0:19:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很有意思吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.32,0:19:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也刚好可以拿你\N来试一试我的新招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.16,0:19:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魍魉丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金刚枪破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.94,0:19:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.51,0:19:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经解决掉了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.84,0:19:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.15,0:19:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.28,0:19:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么好奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.02,0:19:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个魍魉丸\N可是集千万妖怪创造出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让他飞可是一点也不困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.39,0:20:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁感到奇怪了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.46,0:20:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙不就也只会飞起来躲嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.86,0:20:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有本事\N把我的金刚枪破弹回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.44,0:20:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再接我一招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.94,0:20:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金刚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.88,0:20:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就快要被\N魍魉丸的残骸吞掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.65,0:20:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有本事吞掉我的话\N就试试看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金刚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.36,0:20:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.73,0:20:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被挣开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.14,0:20:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白童子在保护魍魉丸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.34,0:20:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.92,0:21:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师\N弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我没有受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.12,0:21:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  好像还是被得逞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.13,0:21:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.73,0:21:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身上的妖气结晶被拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.03,0:21:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.37,0:21:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是寻找不妖璧的重要线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.87,0:21:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要弥勒法师没事就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.14,0:21:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定还有别的\N寻找奈落的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.44,0:21:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是\N那个魍魉丸的事让我很在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.21,0:21:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白童子竟然\N奋不顾身地去保护他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.88,0:21:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这其中一定有什么\N不希望他被杀掉的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.19,0:21:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我照你所说的\N把妖气结晶抢过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.80,0:21:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把魍魉丸留下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.67,0:21:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你怎么使唤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.37,0:21:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魍魉丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.98,0:21:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我为你注入灵魂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.32,0:22:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brand-New World 全新梦想的起点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.26,0:22:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝向目标持续旅程 直到最后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.27,0:22:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brand-New Mind 怀抱热情直到下一扇门扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.54,0:22:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲向未知的世界 快奔驰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.09,0:22:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸手触摸 那微尘般的希望之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.72,0:22:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使勉强握住 横冲直撞的我们想往何处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.57,0:22:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保有自我 Let's go and Try 前进吧 使命只有One way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.57,0:23:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺其自然 Do it!Ready? 最后愿望将达成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.81,0:23:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brand-New World 全新梦想的起点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.79,0:23:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝向目标持续旅程 直到最后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.83,0:23:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brand-New Mind 怀抱热情直到下一扇门扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.10,0:23:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲向未知的世界 快奔驰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.52,0:23:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了寻找桔梗\N追赶杀生丸的奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.03,0:23:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一能消灭他的方法\N就是找到他的心脏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.33,0:23:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛奈落的神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.80,0:23:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要告诉我们\N他的心脏在哪里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.30,0:23:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到\N我们却被引诱到鬼腹之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.70,0:23:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你们几个\N在鬼的体内溶化殆尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.80,0:23:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只留下四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.64,0:24:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是生还是死\N这将是最后的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.81,0:24:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.08,0:24:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人的羁绊\N使用四魂之玉碎片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.55,0:24:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.68,0:24:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你的支持


